{"tha-ap393:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap393:0.2":"Pilindavacchavagga ","tha-ap393:0.3":"Pilindavacchattheraapadana ","tha-ap393:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap393:1.2":"asim dovariko aham; ","tha-ap393:1.3":"Akkhobham amitam bhogam, ","tha-ap393:1.4":"ghare sannicitam mama. ","tha-ap393:2.1":"Rahogato nisiditva, ","tha-ap393:2.2":"pahamsitvana manasam; ","tha-ap393:2.3":"Nisajja pasadavare, ","tha-ap393:2.4":"evam cintesaham tada. ","tha-ap393:3.0":"1.1. Cintanakara ","tha-ap393:3.1":"‘Bahu medhigata bhoga, ","tha-ap393:3.2":"phitam antepuram mama; ","tha-ap393:3.3":"Rajapi sannimantesi, ","tha-ap393:3.4":"anando pathavissaro. ","tha-ap393:4.1":"Ayanca buddho uppanno, ","tha-ap393:4.2":"adhiccuppattiko muni; ","tha-ap393:4.3":"Samvijjanti ca me bhoga, ","tha-ap393:4.4":"danam dassami satthuno. ","tha-ap393:5.1":"Padumena rajaputtena, ","tha-ap393:5.2":"dinnam danavaram jine; ","tha-ap393:5.3":"Hatthinage ca pallanke, ","tha-ap393:5.4":"apassenancanappakam. ","tha-ap393:6.1":"Ahampi danam dassami, ","tha-ap393:6.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:6.3":"Adinnapubbamannesam, ","tha-ap393:6.4":"bhavissam adikammiko. ","tha-ap393:7.1":"Cintetvaham bahuvidham, ","tha-ap393:7.2":"yage yassa sukhamphalam; ","tha-ap393:7.3":"Parikkharadanamaddakkhim, ","tha-ap393:7.4":"mama sankappapuranam. ","tha-ap393:8.1":"Parikkharani dassami, ","tha-ap393:8.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:8.3":"Adinnapubbamannesam, ","tha-ap393:8.4":"bhavissam adikammiko’. ","tha-ap393:9.0":"1.2. Danavatthusampadana ","tha-ap393:9.1":"Nalakare upagamma, ","tha-ap393:9.2":"chattam karesi tavade; ","tha-ap393:9.3":"Chattasatasahassani, ","tha-ap393:9.4":"ekato sannipatayim. ","tha-ap393:10.1":"Dussasatasahassani, ","tha-ap393:10.2":"ekato sannipatayim; ","tha-ap393:10.3":"Pattasatasahassani, ","tha-ap393:10.4":"ekato sannipatayim. ","tha-ap393:11.1":"Vasiyo satthake capi, ","tha-ap393:11.2":"suciyo nakhachedane; ","tha-ap393:11.3":"Hetthachatte thapapesim, ","tha-ap393:11.4":"karetva tadanucchave. ","tha-ap393:12.1":"Vidhupane talavante, ","tha-ap393:12.2":"morahatthe ca camare; ","tha-ap393:12.3":"Parissavane teladhare, ","tha-ap393:12.4":"karayim tadanucchave. ","tha-ap393:13.1":"Sucighare amsabaddhe, ","tha-ap393:13.2":"athopi kayabandhane; ","tha-ap393:13.3":"Adharake ca sukate, ","tha-ap393:13.4":"karayim tadanucchave. ","tha-ap393:14.1":"Paribhogabhajane ca, ","tha-ap393:14.2":"athopi lohathalake; ","tha-ap393:14.3":"Bhesajje purayitvana, ","tha-ap393:14.4":"hetthachatte thapesaham. ","tha-ap393:15.1":"Vacam usiram latthimadhum, ","tha-ap393:15.2":"pipphali maricani ca; ","tha-ap393:15.3":"Haritakim singiveram, ","tha-ap393:15.4":"sabbam puresi bhajane. ","tha-ap393:16.1":"Upahana padukayo, ","tha-ap393:16.2":"atho udakapunchane; ","tha-ap393:16.3":"Kattaradande sukate, ","tha-ap393:16.4":"karayim tadanucchave. ","tha-ap393:17.1":"Osadhanjananali ca, ","tha-ap393:17.2":"salaka dhammakuttara; ","tha-ap393:17.3":"Kuncika pancavannehi, ","tha-ap393:17.4":"sibbite kuncikaghare. ","tha-ap393:18.1":"Ayoge dhumanette ca, ","tha-ap393:18.2":"athopi dipadharake; ","tha-ap393:18.3":"Tumbake ca karande ca, ","tha-ap393:18.4":"karayim tadanucchave. ","tha-ap393:19.1":"Sandase pipphale ceva, ","tha-ap393:19.2":"athopi malaharake; ","tha-ap393:19.3":"Bhesajjathavike ceva, ","tha-ap393:19.4":"karayim tadanucchave. ","tha-ap393:20.1":"Asandiyo pithake ca, ","tha-ap393:20.2":"pallanke caturomaye; ","tha-ap393:20.3":"Tadanucchave karayitva, ","tha-ap393:20.4":"hetthachatte thapesaham. ","tha-ap393:21.1":"Unnabhisi tulabhisi, ","tha-ap393:21.2":"athopi pithikabhisi; ","tha-ap393:21.3":"Bimbohane ca sukate, ","tha-ap393:21.4":"karayim tadanucchave. ","tha-ap393:22.1":"Kuruvinde madhusitthe, ","tha-ap393:22.2":"telam hatthappatapakam; ","tha-ap393:22.3":"Sipatiphalake suci, ","tha-ap393:22.4":"mancam attharanena ca. ","tha-ap393:23.1":"Senasane padapunche, ","tha-ap393:23.2":"sayanasanadandake; ","tha-ap393:23.3":"Dantapone ca atali, ","tha-ap393:23.4":"sisalepanagandhake. ","tha-ap393:24.1":"Arani phalapithe ca, ","tha-ap393:24.2":"pattapidhanathalake; ","tha-ap393:24.3":"Udakassa katacchu ca, ","tha-ap393:24.4":"cunnakam rajanambanam. ","tha-ap393:25.1":"Sammajjanam udapattam, ","tha-ap393:25.2":"tatha vassikasatikam; ","tha-ap393:25.3":"Nisidanam kanducchadi, ","tha-ap393:25.4":"atha antaravasakam. ","tha-ap393:26.1":"Uttarasangasanghati, ","tha-ap393:26.2":"natthukam mukhasodhanam; ","tha-ap393:26.3":"Bilangalonam pahutanca, ","tha-ap393:26.4":"madhunca dadhipanakam. ","tha-ap393:27.1":"Dhupam sittham pilotinca, ","tha-ap393:27.2":"mukhapunchanasuttakam; ","tha-ap393:27.3":"Databbam nama yam atthi, ","tha-ap393:27.4":"yanca kappati satthuno. ","tha-ap393:28.1":"Sabbametam samanetva, ","tha-ap393:28.2":"anandam upasankamim; ","tha-ap393:28.3":"Upasankamma rajanam, ","tha-ap393:28.4":"janetaram mahesino; ","tha-ap393:28.5":"Sirasa abhivadetva, ","tha-ap393:28.6":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap393:29.0":"1.3. Danokasayacana ","tha-ap393:29.1":"‘Ekato jatasamvaddha, ","tha-ap393:29.2":"ubhinnam ekato manam; ","tha-ap393:29.3":"Sadharana sukhadukkhe, ","tha-ap393:29.4":"ubho ca anuvattaka. ","tha-ap393:30.1":"Atthi cetasikam dukkham, ","tha-ap393:30.2":"tavadheyyam arindama; ","tha-ap393:30.3":"Yadi sakkosi tam dukkham, ","tha-ap393:30.4":"vinodeyyasi khattiya’. ","tha-ap393:31.1":"‘Tava dukkham mama dukkham, ","tha-ap393:31.2":"Ubhinnam ekato mano; ","tha-ap393:31.3":"Nitthitanti vijanahi, ","tha-ap393:31.4":"Mamadheyyam sace tuvam’. ","tha-ap393:32.1":"‘Janahi kho maharaja, ","tha-ap393:32.2":"dukkham me dubbinodayam; ","tha-ap393:32.3":"Pahu samano gajjasu, ","tha-ap393:32.4":"ekam te duccajam varam. ","tha-ap393:33.1":"Yavata vijite atthi, ","tha-ap393:33.2":"yavata mama jivitam; ","tha-ap393:33.3":"Etehi yadi te attho, ","tha-ap393:33.4":"dassami avikampito. ","tha-ap393:34.1":"Gajjitam kho taya deva, ","tha-ap393:34.2":"miccha tam bahu gajjitam; ","tha-ap393:34.3":"Janissami tuvam ajja, ","tha-ap393:34.4":"sabbadhamme patitthitam’. ","tha-ap393:35.1":"‘Atibalham nipilesi, ","tha-ap393:35.2":"dadamanassa me sato; ","tha-ap393:35.3":"Kim te me pilitenattho, ","tha-ap393:35.4":"patthitam te kathehi me’. ","tha-ap393:36.1":"‘Icchamaham maharaja, ","tha-ap393:36.2":"buddhasettham anuttaram; ","tha-ap393:36.3":"Bhojayissami sambuddham, ","tha-ap393:36.4":"vajjam me mahu jivitam’. ","tha-ap393:37.1":"‘Annam teham varam dammi, ","tha-ap393:37.2":"ma yacittho tathagatam; ","tha-ap393:37.3":"Adeyyo kassaci buddho, ","tha-ap393:37.4":"mani jotiraso yatha’. ","tha-ap393:38.1":"‘Nanu te gajjitam deva, ","tha-ap393:38.2":"yava jivitamattano; ","tha-ap393:38.3":"Jivitam dadamanena, ","tha-ap393:38.4":"yuttam datum tathagatam’. ","tha-ap393:39.1":"‘Thapaniyo mahaviro, ","tha-ap393:39.2":"adeyyo kassaci jino; ","tha-ap393:39.3":"Na me patissuto buddho, ","tha-ap393:39.4":"varassu amitam dhanam’. ","tha-ap393:40.1":"‘Vinicchayam papunama, ","tha-ap393:40.2":"pucchissama vinicchaye; ","tha-ap393:40.3":"Yathasantham kathessanti, ","tha-ap393:40.4":"patipucchama tam tatha’. ","tha-ap393:41.1":"Ranno hatthe gahetvana, ","tha-ap393:41.2":"agamasim vinicchayam; ","tha-ap393:41.3":"Purato akkhadassanam, ","tha-ap393:41.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap393:42.1":"‘Sunantu me akkhadassa, ","tha-ap393:42.2":"raja varamadasi me; ","tha-ap393:42.3":"Na kinci thapayitvana, ","tha-ap393:42.4":"jivitampi pavarayi. ","tha-ap393:43.1":"Tassa me varadinnassa, ","tha-ap393:43.2":"buddhasettham varim aham; ","tha-ap393:43.3":"Sudinno hoti me buddho, ","tha-ap393:43.4":"chindatha samsayam mama’. ","tha-ap393:44.1":"‘Sossama tava vacanam, ","tha-ap393:44.2":"bhumipalassa rajino; ","tha-ap393:44.3":"Ubhinnam vacanam sutva, ","tha-ap393:44.4":"chindissamettha samsayam. ","tha-ap393:45.1":"Sabbam deva taya dinnam, ","tha-ap393:45.2":"imassa sabbagahikam; ","tha-ap393:45.3":"Na kinci thapayitvana, ","tha-ap393:45.4":"jivitampi pavarayi’. ","tha-ap393:46.1":"‘Kicchappattova hutvana, ","tha-ap393:46.2":"yaci varamanuttaram; ","tha-ap393:46.3":"Imam sudukkhitam natva, ","tha-ap393:46.4":"adasim sabbagahikam’. ","tha-ap393:47.1":"‘Parajayo tuvam deva, ","tha-ap393:47.2":"assa deyyo tathagato; ","tha-ap393:47.3":"Ubhinnam samsayo chinno, ","tha-ap393:47.4":"yathasanthamhi titthatha’. ","tha-ap393:48.1":"Raja tattheva thatvana, ","tha-ap393:48.2":"akkhadassetadabravi; ","tha-ap393:48.3":"‘Samma mayhampi deyyatha, ","tha-ap393:48.4":"puna buddham labhamaham’. ","tha-ap393:49.1":"‘Puretva tava sankappam, ","tha-ap393:49.2":"bhojayitva tathagatam; ","tha-ap393:49.3":"Puna deyyasi sambuddham, ","tha-ap393:49.4":"anandassa yasassino’. ","tha-ap393:50.0":"1.4. Nimantanakatha ","tha-ap393:50.1":"Akkhadassebhivadetva, ","tha-ap393:50.2":"anandancapi khattiyam; ","tha-ap393:50.3":"Tuttho pamudito hutva, ","tha-ap393:50.4":"sambuddhamupasankamim. ","tha-ap393:51.1":"Upasankamma sambuddham, ","tha-ap393:51.2":"oghatinnamanasavam; ","tha-ap393:51.3":"Sirasa abhivadetva, ","tha-ap393:51.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap393:52.1":"‘Vasisatasahassehi, ","tha-ap393:52.2":"adhivasehi cakkhuma; ","tha-ap393:52.3":"Hasayanto mama cittam, ","tha-ap393:52.4":"nivesanamupehi me’. ","tha-ap393:53.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap393:53.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap393:53.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap393:53.4":"adhivasesi cakkhuma. ","tha-ap393:54.1":"Adhivasanamannaya, ","tha-ap393:54.2":"abhivadiya satthuno; ","tha-ap393:54.3":"Hattho udaggacittoham, ","tha-ap393:54.4":"nivesanamupagamim. ","tha-ap393:55.0":"1.5. Danapatiyadana ","tha-ap393:55.1":"Mittamacce samanetva, ","tha-ap393:55.2":"idam vacanamabravim; ","tha-ap393:55.3":"‘Sudullabho maya laddho, ","tha-ap393:55.4":"mani jotiraso yatha. ","tha-ap393:56.1":"Kena tam pujayissama, ","tha-ap393:56.2":"appameyyo anupamo; ","tha-ap393:56.3":"Atulo asamo dhiro, ","tha-ap393:56.4":"jino appatipuggalo. ","tha-ap393:57.1":"Tathasamasamo ceva, ","tha-ap393:57.2":"adutiyo narasabho; ","tha-ap393:57.3":"Dukkaram adhikaranhi, ","tha-ap393:57.4":"buddhanucchavikam maya. ","tha-ap393:58.1":"Nanapupphe samanetva, ","tha-ap393:58.2":"karoma pupphamandapam; ","tha-ap393:58.3":"Buddhanucchavikam etam, ","tha-ap393:58.4":"sabbapuja bhavissati’. ","tha-ap393:59.1":"Uppalam padumam vapi, ","tha-ap393:59.2":"vassikam adhimuttakam; ","tha-ap393:59.3":"Campakam nagapupphanca, ","tha-ap393:59.4":"mandapam karayim aham. ","tha-ap393:60.1":"Satasanasahassani, ","tha-ap393:60.2":"chattacchayaya pannapim; ","tha-ap393:60.3":"Pacchimam asanam mayham, ","tha-ap393:60.4":"adhikam satamagghati. ","tha-ap393:61.1":"Satasanasahassani, ","tha-ap393:61.2":"chattacchayaya pannapim; ","tha-ap393:61.3":"Patiyadetva annapanam, ","tha-ap393:61.4":"kalam arocayim aham. ","tha-ap393:62.1":"Arocitamhi kalamhi, ","tha-ap393:62.2":"padumuttaro mahamuni; ","tha-ap393:62.3":"Vasisatasahassehi, ","tha-ap393:62.4":"nivesanamupesi me. ","tha-ap393:63.1":"Dharentam uparicchattam, ","tha-ap393:63.2":"suphullapupphamandape; ","tha-ap393:63.3":"Vasisatasahassehi, ","tha-ap393:63.4":"nisidi purisuttamo. ","tha-ap393:64.1":"‘Chattasatasahassani, ","tha-ap393:64.2":"satasahassamasanam; ","tha-ap393:64.3":"Kappiyam anavajjanca, ","tha-ap393:64.4":"patiganhahi cakkhuma’. ","tha-ap393:65.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap393:65.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap393:65.3":"Mamam taretukamo so, ","tha-ap393:65.4":"sampaticchi mahamuni. ","tha-ap393:66.0":"1.6. Danakatha ","tha-ap393:66.1":"Bhikkhuno ekamekassa, ","tha-ap393:66.2":"Paccekam pattamadasaham; ","tha-ap393:66.3":"Jahimsu sumbhakam pattam, ","tha-ap393:66.4":"Lohapattam adharayum. ","tha-ap393:67.1":"Sattarattindivam buddho, ","tha-ap393:67.2":"nisidi pupphamandape; ","tha-ap393:67.3":"Bodhayanto bahu satte, ","tha-ap393:67.4":"dhammacakkam pavattayi. ","tha-ap393:68.1":"Dhammacakkam pavattento, ","tha-ap393:68.2":"hetthato pupphamandape; ","tha-ap393:68.3":"Cullasitisahassanam, ","tha-ap393:68.4":"dhammabhisamayo ahu. ","tha-ap393:69.1":"Sattame divase patte, ","tha-ap393:69.2":"padumuttaro mahamuni; ","tha-ap393:69.3":"Chattacchayayamasino, ","tha-ap393:69.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap393:70.0":"1.7. Byakarana ","tha-ap393:70.1":"‘Anunakam danavaram, ","tha-ap393:70.2":"yo me padasi manavo; ","tha-ap393:70.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap393:70.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap393:71.1":"Hatthi assa ratha patti, ","tha-ap393:71.2":"sena ca caturangini; ","tha-ap393:71.3":"Parivaressantimam niccam, ","tha-ap393:71.4":"sabbadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:72.1":"Hatthiyanam assayanam, ","tha-ap393:72.2":"sivika sandamanika; ","tha-ap393:72.3":"Upatthissantimam niccam, ","tha-ap393:72.4":"sabbadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:73.1":"Satthi rathasahassani, ","tha-ap393:73.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","tha-ap393:73.3":"Parivaressantimam niccam, ","tha-ap393:73.4":"sabbadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:74.1":"Satthi turiyasahassani, ","tha-ap393:74.2":"bheriyo samalankata; ","tha-ap393:74.3":"Vajjayissantimam niccam, ","tha-ap393:74.4":"sabbadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:75.1":"Chalasitisahassani, ","tha-ap393:75.2":"nariyo samalankata; ","tha-ap393:75.3":"Vicittavatthabharana, ","tha-ap393:75.4":"amukkamanikundala. ","tha-ap393:76.1":"Alarapamha hasula, ","tha-ap393:76.2":"susanna tanumajjhima; ","tha-ap393:76.3":"Parivaressantimam niccam, ","tha-ap393:76.4":"sabbadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:77.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap393:77.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap393:77.3":"Sahassakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap393:77.4":"devarajjam karissati. ","tha-ap393:78.1":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap393:78.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap393:78.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap393:78.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap393:79.1":"Devaloke vasantassa, ","tha-ap393:79.2":"punnakammasamangino; ","tha-ap393:79.3":"Devalokapariyantam, ","tha-ap393:79.4":"ratanachattam dharissati. ","tha-ap393:80.1":"Icchissati yada chayam, ","tha-ap393:80.2":"chadanam dussapupphajam; ","tha-ap393:80.3":"Imassa cittamannaya, ","tha-ap393:80.4":"nibaddham chadayissati. ","tha-ap393:81.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap393:81.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap393:81.3":"Punnakammena samyutto, ","tha-ap393:81.4":"brahmabandhu bhavissati. ","tha-ap393:82.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap393:82.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap393:82.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap393:82.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap393:83.1":"Sabbametam abhinnaya, ","tha-ap393:83.2":"gotamo sakyapungavo; ","tha-ap393:83.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap393:83.4":"etadagge thapessati. ","tha-ap393:84.1":"Pilindavacchanamena, ","tha-ap393:84.2":"hessati satthusavako; ","tha-ap393:84.3":"Devanam asurananca, ","tha-ap393:84.4":"gandhabbananca sakkato. ","tha-ap393:85.1":"Bhikkhunam bhikkhuninanca, ","tha-ap393:85.2":"gihinanca tatheva so; ","tha-ap393:85.3":"Piyo hutvana sabbesam, ","tha-ap393:85.4":"viharissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap393:86.0":"1.8. Dananisamsakatha ","tha-ap393:86.1":"Satasahasse katam kammam, ","tha-ap393:86.2":"phalam dassesi me idha; ","tha-ap393:86.3":"Sumutto saravegova, ","tha-ap393:86.4":"kilese jhapayi mama. ","tha-ap393:87.1":"Aho me sukatam kammam, ","tha-ap393:87.2":"punnakkhette anuttare; ","tha-ap393:87.3":"Yattha karam karitvana, ","tha-ap393:87.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap393:88.1":"Anunakam danavaram, ","tha-ap393:88.2":"adasi yo hi manavo; ","tha-ap393:88.3":"Adipubbangamo asi, ","tha-ap393:88.4":"tassa danassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:89.0":"1.8.1. Chattanisamsa ","tha-ap393:89.1":"Chatte ca sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:89.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:89.3":"Atthanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:89.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:90.1":"Sitam unham na janami, ","tha-ap393:90.2":"rajojallam na limpati; ","tha-ap393:90.3":"Anupaddavo aniti ca, ","tha-ap393:90.4":"homi apacito sada. ","tha-ap393:91.1":"Sukhumacchaviko homi, ","tha-ap393:91.2":"visadam hoti manasam; ","tha-ap393:91.3":"Chattasatasahassani, ","tha-ap393:91.4":"bhave samsarato mama. ","tha-ap393:92.1":"Sabbalankarayuttani, ","tha-ap393:92.2":"tassa kammassa vahasa; ","tha-ap393:92.3":"Imam jatim thapetvana, ","tha-ap393:92.4":"matthake dharayanti me. ","tha-ap393:93.1":"Kasma imaya jatiya, ","tha-ap393:93.2":"natthi me chattadharana; ","tha-ap393:93.3":"Mama sabbam katam kammam, ","tha-ap393:93.4":"vimuttichattapattiya. ","tha-ap393:94.0":"1.8.2. Dussanisamsa ","tha-ap393:94.1":"Dussani sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:94.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:94.3":"Atthanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:94.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:95.1":"Suvannavanno virajo, ","tha-ap393:95.2":"sappabhaso patapava; ","tha-ap393:95.3":"Siniddham hoti me gattam, ","tha-ap393:95.4":"bhave samsarato mama. ","tha-ap393:96.1":"Dussasatasahassani, ","tha-ap393:96.2":"seta pita ca lohita; ","tha-ap393:96.3":"Dharenti matthake mayham, ","tha-ap393:96.4":"dussadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:97.1":"Koseyyakambaliyani, ","tha-ap393:97.2":"khomakappasikani ca; ","tha-ap393:97.3":"Sabbattha patilabhami, ","tha-ap393:97.4":"tesam nissandato aham. ","tha-ap393:98.0":"1.8.3. Pattanisamsa ","tha-ap393:98.1":"Patte sugate datvana, ","tha-ap393:98.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:98.3":"Dasanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:98.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:99.1":"Suvannathale manithale, ","tha-ap393:99.2":"rajatepi ca thalake; ","tha-ap393:99.3":"Lohitangamaye thale, ","tha-ap393:99.4":"paribhunjami sabbada. ","tha-ap393:100.1":"Anupaddavo aniti ca, ","tha-ap393:100.2":"homi apacito sada; ","tha-ap393:100.3":"Labhi annassa panassa, ","tha-ap393:100.4":"vatthassa sayanassa ca. ","tha-ap393:101.1":"Na vinassanti me bhoga, ","tha-ap393:101.2":"thitacitto bhavamaham; ","tha-ap393:101.3":"Dhammakamo sada homi, ","tha-ap393:101.4":"appakleso anasavo. ","tha-ap393:102.1":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap393:102.2":"anubandha ime guna; ","tha-ap393:102.3":"Chaya yathapi rukkhassa, ","tha-ap393:102.4":"sabbattha na jahanti mam. ","tha-ap393:103.0":"1.8.4. Vasianisamsa ","tha-ap393:103.1":"Cittabandhanasambaddha, ","tha-ap393:103.2":"sukata vasiyo bahu; ","tha-ap393:103.3":"Datvana buddhasetthassa, ","tha-ap393:103.4":"sanghassa ca tathevaham. ","tha-ap393:104.1":"Atthanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:104.2":"kammanucchavike mama; ","tha-ap393:104.3":"Suro homavisari ca, ","tha-ap393:104.4":"vesarajjesu parami. ","tha-ap393:105.1":"Dhitiviriyava homi, ","tha-ap393:105.2":"paggahitamano sada; ","tha-ap393:105.3":"Kilesacchedanam nanam, ","tha-ap393:105.4":"sukhumam atulam sucim; ","tha-ap393:105.5":"Sabbattha patilabhami, ","tha-ap393:105.6":"tassa nissandato aham. ","tha-ap393:106.0":"1.8.5. Satthakanisamsa ","tha-ap393:106.1":"Akakkase apharuse, ","tha-ap393:106.2":"sudhote satthake bahu; ","tha-ap393:106.3":"Pasannacitto datvana, ","tha-ap393:106.4":"buddhe sanghe tatheva ca. ","tha-ap393:107.1":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:107.2":"kammanucchavike mama; ","tha-ap393:107.3":"Kalyanamittam viriyam, ","tha-ap393:107.4":"khantinca mettasatthakam. ","tha-ap393:108.1":"Tanhasallassa chinnatta, ","tha-ap393:108.2":"pannasattham anuttaram; ","tha-ap393:108.3":"Vajirena samam nanam, ","tha-ap393:108.4":"tesam nissandato labhe. ","tha-ap393:109.0":"1.8.6. Sucianisamsa ","tha-ap393:109.1":"Suciyo sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:109.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:109.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:109.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:110.1":"Na samsayo kankhacchedo, ","tha-ap393:110.2":"abhirupo ca bhogava; ","tha-ap393:110.3":"Tikkhapanno sada homi, ","tha-ap393:110.4":"samsaranto bhavabhave. ","tha-ap393:111.1":"Gambhiram nipunam thanam, ","tha-ap393:111.2":"attham nanena passayim; ","tha-ap393:111.3":"Vajiraggasamam nanam, ","tha-ap393:111.4":"hoti me tamaghatanam. ","tha-ap393:112.0":"1.8.7. Nakhacchedananisamsa ","tha-ap393:112.1":"Nakhacchedane sugate, ","tha-ap393:112.2":"datva sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:112.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:112.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:113.1":"Dasidase gavasse ca, ","tha-ap393:113.2":"bhatake natake bahu; ","tha-ap393:113.3":"Nhapite bhattake sude, ","tha-ap393:113.4":"sabbattheva labhamaham. ","tha-ap393:114.0":"1.8.8. Vidhupanatalavantanisamsa ","tha-ap393:114.1":"Vidhupane sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:114.2":"talavante ca sobhane; ","tha-ap393:114.3":"Atthanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:114.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:115.1":"Sitam unham na janami, ","tha-ap393:115.2":"parilaho na vijjati; ","tha-ap393:115.3":"Daratham nabhijanami, ","tha-ap393:115.4":"cittasantapanam mama. ","tha-ap393:116.1":"Ragaggi dosamohaggi, ","tha-ap393:116.2":"managgi ditthiaggi ca; ","tha-ap393:116.3":"Sabbaggi nibbuta mayham, ","tha-ap393:116.4":"tassa nissandato mama. ","tha-ap393:117.0":"1.8.9. Morahattha-camara ","tha-ap393:117.1":"Morahatthe camariyo, ","tha-ap393:117.2":"datva sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:117.3":"Upasantakilesoham, ","tha-ap393:117.4":"viharami anangano. ","tha-ap393:118.0":"1.8.10. Parissavana-dhammakara ","tha-ap393:118.1":"Parissavane sugate, ","tha-ap393:118.2":"datva dhammakaruttame; ","tha-ap393:118.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:118.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:119.1":"Sabbesam samatikkamma, ","tha-ap393:119.2":"dibbam ayum labhamaham; ","tha-ap393:119.3":"Appasayho sada homi, ","tha-ap393:119.4":"corapaccatthikehi va. ","tha-ap393:120.1":"Satthena va visena va, ","tha-ap393:120.2":"vihesampi na kubbate; ","tha-ap393:120.3":"Antaramaranam natthi, ","tha-ap393:120.4":"tesam nissandato mama. ","tha-ap393:121.0":"1.8.11. Teladharanisamsa ","tha-ap393:121.1":"Teladhare sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:121.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:121.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:121.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:122.1":"Sucarurupo subhaddo, ","tha-ap393:122.2":"susamuggatamanaso; ","tha-ap393:122.3":"Avikkhittamano homi, ","tha-ap393:122.4":"sabbarakkhehi rakkhito. ","tha-ap393:123.0":"1.8.12. Sucigharanisamsa ","tha-ap393:123.1":"Sucighare sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:123.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:123.3":"Tinanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:123.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:124.1":"Cetosukham kayasukham, ","tha-ap393:124.2":"iriyapathajam sukham; ","tha-ap393:124.3":"Ime gune patilabhe, ","tha-ap393:124.4":"tassa nissandato aham. ","tha-ap393:125.0":"1.8.13. Amsabaddhanisamsa ","tha-ap393:125.1":"Amsabaddhe jine datva, ","tha-ap393:125.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:125.3":"Tinanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:125.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:126.1":"Saddhamme gadham vindami, ","tha-ap393:126.2":"Sarami dutiyam bhavam; ","tha-ap393:126.3":"Sabbattha succhavi homi, ","tha-ap393:126.4":"Tassa nissandato aham. ","tha-ap393:127.0":"1.8.14. Kayabandhananisamsa ","tha-ap393:127.1":"Kayabandhe jine datva, ","tha-ap393:127.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:127.3":"Chanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:127.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:128.1":"Samadhisu na kampami, ","tha-ap393:128.2":"vasi homi samadhisu; ","tha-ap393:128.3":"Abhejjapariso homi, ","tha-ap393:128.4":"adeyyavacano sada. ","tha-ap393:129.1":"Upatthitasati homi, ","tha-ap393:129.2":"taso mayham na vijjati; ","tha-ap393:129.3":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap393:129.4":"anubandha ime guna. ","tha-ap393:130.0":"1.8.15. Adharakanisamsa ","tha-ap393:130.1":"Adharake jine datva, ","tha-ap393:130.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:130.3":"Pancavannehi dayado, ","tha-ap393:130.4":"acalo homi kenaci. ","tha-ap393:131.1":"Ye keci me suta dhamma, ","tha-ap393:131.2":"satinanappabodhana; ","tha-ap393:131.3":"Dhata me na vinassanti, ","tha-ap393:131.4":"bhavanti suvinicchita. ","tha-ap393:132.0":"1.8.16. Bhajananisamsa ","tha-ap393:132.1":"Bhajane paribhoge ca, ","tha-ap393:132.2":"datva buddhe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:132.3":"Tinanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:132.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:133.1":"Sonnamaye manimaye, ","tha-ap393:133.2":"athopi phalikamaye; ","tha-ap393:133.3":"Lohitangamaye ceva, ","tha-ap393:133.4":"labhami bhajane aham. ","tha-ap393:134.1":"Bhariya dasadasi ca, ","tha-ap393:134.2":"hatthissarathapattike; ","tha-ap393:134.3":"Itthi patibbata ceva, ","tha-ap393:134.4":"paribhogani sabbada. ","tha-ap393:135.1":"Vijja mantapade ceva, ","tha-ap393:135.2":"vividhe agame bahu; ","tha-ap393:135.3":"Sabbam sippam nisamemi, ","tha-ap393:135.4":"paribhogani sabbada. ","tha-ap393:136.0":"1.8.17. Thalakanisamsa ","tha-ap393:136.1":"Thalake sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:136.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:136.3":"Tinanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:136.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:137.1":"Sonnamaye manimaye, ","tha-ap393:137.2":"athopi phalikamaye; ","tha-ap393:137.3":"Lohitangamaye ceva, ","tha-ap393:137.4":"labhami thalake aham. ","tha-ap393:138.1":"Asatthake phalamaye, ","tha-ap393:138.2":"atho pokkharapattake; ","tha-ap393:138.3":"Madhupanakasankhe ca, ","tha-ap393:138.4":"labhami thalake aham. ","tha-ap393:139.1":"Vatte gune patipatti, ","tha-ap393:139.2":"acarakiriyasu ca; ","tha-ap393:139.3":"Ime gune patilabhe, ","tha-ap393:139.4":"tassa nissandato aham. ","tha-ap393:140.0":"1.8.18. Bhesajjanisamsa ","tha-ap393:140.1":"Bhesajjam sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:140.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:140.3":"Dasanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:140.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:141.1":"Ayuva balava dhiro, ","tha-ap393:141.2":"vannava yasava sukhi; ","tha-ap393:141.3":"Anupaddavo aniti ca, ","tha-ap393:141.4":"homi apacito sada; ","tha-ap393:141.5":"Na me piyaviyogatthi, ","tha-ap393:141.6":"tassa nissandato mama. ","tha-ap393:142.0":"1.8.19. Upahananisamsa ","tha-ap393:142.1":"Upahane jine datva, ","tha-ap393:142.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:142.3":"Tinanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:142.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:143.1":"Hatthiyanam assayanam, ","tha-ap393:143.2":"sivika sandamanika; ","tha-ap393:143.3":"Satthisatasahassani, ","tha-ap393:143.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap393:144.1":"Manimaya tambamaya, ","tha-ap393:144.2":"sonnarajatapaduka; ","tha-ap393:144.3":"Nibbattanti paduddhare, ","tha-ap393:144.4":"bhave samsarato mama. ","tha-ap393:145.1":"Niyamam sati dhavanti, ","tha-ap393:145.2":"aguacarasodhanam; ","tha-ap393:145.3":"Ime gune patilabhe, ","tha-ap393:145.4":"tassa nissandato aham. ","tha-ap393:146.0":"1.8.20. Padukanisamsa ","tha-ap393:146.1":"Paduke sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:146.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:146.3":"Iddhipadukamaruyha, ","tha-ap393:146.4":"viharami yadicchakam. ","tha-ap393:147.0":"1.8.21. Udakapunchananisamsa ","tha-ap393:147.1":"Udakapunchanacole, ","tha-ap393:147.2":"datva buddhe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:147.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:147.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:148.1":"Suvannavanno virajo, ","tha-ap393:148.2":"sappabhaso patapava; ","tha-ap393:148.3":"Siniddham hoti me gattam, ","tha-ap393:148.4":"rajojallam na limpati; ","tha-ap393:148.5":"Ime gune patilabhe, ","tha-ap393:148.6":"tassa nissandato aham. ","tha-ap393:149.0":"1.8.22. Kattaradandanisamsa ","tha-ap393:149.1":"Kattaradande sugate, ","tha-ap393:149.2":"datva sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:149.3":"Chanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:149.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:150.1":"Putta mayham bahu honti, ","tha-ap393:150.2":"taso mayham na vijjati; ","tha-ap393:150.3":"Appasayho sada homi, ","tha-ap393:150.4":"sabbarakkhehi rakkhito; ","tha-ap393:150.5":"Khalitampi na janami, ","tha-ap393:150.6":"abhantam manasam mama. ","tha-ap393:151.0":"1.8.23. Osadhanjananisamsa ","tha-ap393:151.1":"Osadham anjanam datva, ","tha-ap393:151.2":"buddhe sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:151.3":"Atthanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:151.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:152.1":"Visalanayano homi, ","tha-ap393:152.2":"setapito ca lohito; ","tha-ap393:152.3":"Anavilapasannakkho, ","tha-ap393:152.4":"sabbarogavivajjito. ","tha-ap393:153.1":"Labhami dibbanayanam, ","tha-ap393:153.2":"pannacakkhum anuttaram; ","tha-ap393:153.3":"Ime gune patilabhe, ","tha-ap393:153.4":"tassa nissandato aham. ","tha-ap393:154.0":"1.8.24. Kuncikanisamsa ","tha-ap393:154.1":"Kuncike sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:154.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:154.3":"Dhammadvaravivaranam, ","tha-ap393:154.4":"labhami nanakuncikam. ","tha-ap393:155.0":"1.8.25. Kuncikagharanisamsa ","tha-ap393:155.1":"Kuncikanam ghare datva, ","tha-ap393:155.2":"buddhe sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:155.3":"Dvanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:155.4":"kammanucchavike mama; ","tha-ap393:155.5":"Appakodho anayaso, ","tha-ap393:155.6":"samsaranto bhave aham. ","tha-ap393:156.0":"1.8.26. Ayoganisamsa ","tha-ap393:156.1":"Ayoge sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:156.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:156.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:156.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:157.1":"Samadhisu na kampami, ","tha-ap393:157.2":"vasi homi samadhisu; ","tha-ap393:157.3":"Abhejjapariso homi, ","tha-ap393:157.4":"adeyyavacano sada; ","tha-ap393:157.5":"Jayati bhogasampatti, ","tha-ap393:157.6":"bhave samsarato mama. ","tha-ap393:158.0":"1.8.27. Dhumanettanisamsa ","tha-ap393:158.1":"Dhumanette jine datva, ","tha-ap393:158.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:158.3":"Tinanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:158.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:159.1":"Sati me ujuka hoti, ","tha-ap393:159.2":"susambandha ca nharavo; ","tha-ap393:159.3":"Labhami dibbanayanam, ","tha-ap393:159.4":"tassa nissandato aham. ","tha-ap393:160.0":"1.8.28. Dipadharanisamsa ","tha-ap393:160.1":"Dipadhare jine datva, ","tha-ap393:160.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:160.3":"Tinanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:160.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:161.1":"Jatima angasampanno, ","tha-ap393:161.2":"pannava buddhasammato; ","tha-ap393:161.3":"Ime gune patilabhe, ","tha-ap393:161.4":"tassa nissandato aham. ","tha-ap393:162.0":"1.8.29. Tumbaka-karanda ","tha-ap393:162.1":"Tumbake ca karande ca, ","tha-ap393:162.2":"datva buddhe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:162.3":"Dasanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:162.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:163.1":"Sugutto sukhasamangi, ","tha-ap393:163.2":"Mahayaso tathagati; ","tha-ap393:163.3":"Vipattivigato sukhumalo, ","tha-ap393:163.4":"Sabbitiparivajjito. ","tha-ap393:164.1":"Vipule ca gune labhi, ","tha-ap393:164.2":"samava calana mama; ","tha-ap393:164.3":"Suvivajjitaubbego, ","tha-ap393:164.4":"tumbake ca karandake. ","tha-ap393:165.1":"Labhami caturo vanne, ","tha-ap393:165.2":"hatthissaratanani ca; ","tha-ap393:165.3":"Tani me na vinassanti, ","tha-ap393:165.4":"tumbadane idam phalam. ","tha-ap393:166.0":"1.8.30. Malaharananisamsa ","tha-ap393:166.1":"Malaharaniyo datva, ","tha-ap393:166.2":"buddhe sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:166.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:166.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:167.1":"Sabbalakkhanasampanno, ","tha-ap393:167.2":"ayupannasamahito; ","tha-ap393:167.3":"Sabbayasavinimutto, ","tha-ap393:167.4":"kayo me hoti sabbada. ","tha-ap393:168.0":"1.8.31. Pipphalanisamsa ","tha-ap393:168.1":"Tanudhare sunisite, ","tha-ap393:168.2":"sanghe datvana pipphale; ","tha-ap393:168.3":"Kilesakantanam nanam, ","tha-ap393:168.4":"labhami atulam sucim. ","tha-ap393:169.0":"1.8.32. Sandasanisamsa ","tha-ap393:169.1":"Sandase sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:169.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:169.3":"Kilesabhanjanam nanam, ","tha-ap393:169.4":"labhami atulam sucim. ","tha-ap393:170.0":"1.8.33. Natthukanisamsa ","tha-ap393:170.1":"Natthuke sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:170.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:170.3":"Atthanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:170.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:171.1":"Saddham silam hirincapi, ","tha-ap393:171.2":"atha ottappiyam gunam; ","tha-ap393:171.3":"Sutam caganca khantinca, ","tha-ap393:171.4":"pannam me atthamam gunam. ","tha-ap393:172.0":"1.8.34. Pithakanisamsa ","tha-ap393:172.1":"Pithake sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:172.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:172.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:172.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:173.1":"Ucce kule pajayami, ","tha-ap393:173.2":"mahabhogo bhavamaham; ","tha-ap393:173.3":"Sabbe mam apacayanti, ","tha-ap393:173.4":"kitti abbhuggata mama. ","tha-ap393:174.1":"Kappasatasahassani, ","tha-ap393:174.2":"pallanka caturassaka; ","tha-ap393:174.3":"Parivarenti mam niccam, ","tha-ap393:174.4":"samvibhagarato aham. ","tha-ap393:175.0":"1.8.35. Bhisianisamsa ","tha-ap393:175.1":"Bhisiyo sugate datva, ","tha-ap393:175.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:175.3":"Chanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:175.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:176.1":"Samasugattopacito, ","tha-ap393:176.2":"muduko carudassano; ","tha-ap393:176.3":"Labhami nanaparivaram, ","tha-ap393:176.4":"bhisidanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:177.1":"Tulika vikatikayo, ","tha-ap393:177.2":"kattissa cittaka bahu; ","tha-ap393:177.3":"Varapotthake kambale ca, ","tha-ap393:177.4":"labhami vividhe aham. ","tha-ap393:178.1":"Pavarike ca muduke, ","tha-ap393:178.2":"mudukajinaveniyo; ","tha-ap393:178.3":"Labhami vividhatthare, ","tha-ap393:178.4":"bhisidanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:179.1":"Yato sarami attanam, ","tha-ap393:179.2":"yato pattosmi vinnutam; ","tha-ap393:179.3":"Atuccho jhanamancomhi, ","tha-ap393:179.4":"bhisidanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:180.0":"1.8.36. Bibbohananisamsa ","tha-ap393:180.1":"Bibbohane jine datva, ","tha-ap393:180.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:180.3":"Chanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:180.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:181.1":"Unnike padumake ca, ","tha-ap393:181.2":"atho lohitacandane; ","tha-ap393:181.3":"Bibbohane upadhemi, ","tha-ap393:181.4":"uttamangam sada mama. ","tha-ap393:182.1":"Atthangike maggavare, ","tha-ap393:182.2":"samanne caturo phale; ","tha-ap393:182.3":"Tesu nanam uppadetva, ","tha-ap393:182.4":"vihare niccakalikam. ","tha-ap393:183.1":"Dane dame samyame ca, ","tha-ap393:183.2":"appamannasu rupisu; ","tha-ap393:183.3":"Tesu nanam uppadetva, ","tha-ap393:183.4":"vihare sabbakalikam. ","tha-ap393:184.1":"Vatte gune patipatti, ","tha-ap393:184.2":"acarakiriyasu ca; ","tha-ap393:184.3":"Tesu nanam uppadetva, ","tha-ap393:184.4":"vihare sabbada aham. ","tha-ap393:185.1":"Cankame va padhane va, ","tha-ap393:185.2":"viriye bodhipakkhiye; ","tha-ap393:185.3":"Tesu nanam uppadetva, ","tha-ap393:185.4":"viharami yadicchakam. ","tha-ap393:186.1":"Silam samadhi panna ca, ","tha-ap393:186.2":"vimutti ca anuttara; ","tha-ap393:186.3":"Tesu nanam uppadetva, ","tha-ap393:186.4":"viharami sukham aham. ","tha-ap393:187.0":"1.8.37. Phalapithanisamsa ","tha-ap393:187.1":"Phalapithe jine datva, ","tha-ap393:187.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:187.3":"Dvanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:187.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:188.1":"Sonnamaye manimaye, ","tha-ap393:188.2":"dantasaramaye bahu; ","tha-ap393:188.3":"Pallankasetthe vindami, ","tha-ap393:188.4":"phalapithassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:189.0":"1.8.38. Padapithanisamsa ","tha-ap393:189.1":"Padapithe jine datva, ","tha-ap393:189.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:189.3":"Dvanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:189.4":"kammanucchavike mama; ","tha-ap393:189.5":"Labhami bahuke yane, ","tha-ap393:189.6":"padapithassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:190.1":"Dasi dasa ca bhariya, ","tha-ap393:190.2":"ye canne anujivino; ","tha-ap393:190.3":"Samma paricarante mam, ","tha-ap393:190.4":"padapithassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:191.0":"1.8.39. Telabbhanjananisamsa ","tha-ap393:191.1":"Telaabbhanjane datva, ","tha-ap393:191.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:191.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:191.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:192.1":"Abyadhita rupavata, ","tha-ap393:192.2":"khippam dhammanisantita; ","tha-ap393:192.3":"Labhita annapanassa, ","tha-ap393:192.4":"ayupancamakam mama. ","tha-ap393:193.0":"1.8.40. Sappitelanisamsa ","tha-ap393:193.1":"Sappitelanca datvana, ","tha-ap393:193.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:193.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:193.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:194.1":"Thamava rupasampanno, ","tha-ap393:194.2":"pahatthatanujo sada; ","tha-ap393:194.3":"Abyadhi visado homi, ","tha-ap393:194.4":"sappitelassidam phalam. ","tha-ap393:195.0":"1.8.41. Mukhasodhanakanisamsa ","tha-ap393:195.1":"Mukhasodhanakam datva, ","tha-ap393:195.2":"buddhe sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:195.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:195.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:196.1":"Visuddhakantho madhurassaro, ","tha-ap393:196.2":"Kasasasavivajjito; ","tha-ap393:196.3":"Uppalagandho mukhato, ","tha-ap393:196.4":"Upavayati me sada. ","tha-ap393:197.0":"1.8.42. Dadhianisamsa ","tha-ap393:197.1":"Dadhim datvana sampannam, ","tha-ap393:197.2":"buddhe sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:197.3":"Bhunjami amatam bhattam, ","tha-ap393:197.4":"varam kayagatasatim. ","tha-ap393:198.0":"1.8.43. Madhuanisamsa ","tha-ap393:198.1":"Vannagandharasopetam, ","tha-ap393:198.2":"madhum datva jine gane; ","tha-ap393:198.3":"Anupamam atuliyam, ","tha-ap393:198.4":"pive muttirasam aham. ","tha-ap393:199.0":"1.8.44. Rasanisamsa ","tha-ap393:199.1":"Yathabhutam rasam datva, ","tha-ap393:199.2":"buddhe sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:199.3":"Caturo phale anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:199.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:200.0":"1.8.45. Annapananisamsa ","tha-ap393:200.1":"Annam pananca datvana, ","tha-ap393:200.2":"buddhe sanghe ganuttame; ","tha-ap393:200.3":"Dasanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:200.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:201.1":"Ayuva balava dhiro, ","tha-ap393:201.2":"vannava yasava sukhi; ","tha-ap393:201.3":"Labhi annassa panassa, ","tha-ap393:201.4":"suro pannanava sada; ","tha-ap393:201.5":"Ime gune patilabhe, ","tha-ap393:201.6":"samsaranto bhave aham. ","tha-ap393:202.0":"1.8.46. Dhupanisamsa ","tha-ap393:202.1":"Dhupam datvana sugate, ","tha-ap393:202.2":"sanghe ganavaruttame; ","tha-ap393:202.3":"Dasanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap393:202.4":"kammanucchavike mama. ","tha-ap393:203.1":"Sugandhadeho yasava, ","tha-ap393:203.2":"sighapanno ca kittima; ","tha-ap393:203.3":"Tikkhapanno bhuripanno, ","tha-ap393:203.4":"hasagambhirapannava. ","tha-ap393:204.1":"Vepullajavanapanno, ","tha-ap393:204.2":"samsaranto bhavabhave; ","tha-ap393:204.3":"Tasseva vahasa dani, ","tha-ap393:204.4":"patto santisukham sivam. ","tha-ap393:205.0":"1.9. Sadharananisamsa ","tha-ap393:205.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap393:205.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap393:205.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap393:205.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap393:206.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap393:206.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap393:206.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap393:206.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap393:207.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap393:207.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap393:207.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap393:207.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap393:208.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pilindavaccho thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap393:209.1":"Pilindavacchattherassapadanam pathamam. "}